data.description: Welcome to 309 Cedar Lane in Conway! This charming 4-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom residence sits on a spacious .30-acre lot and comes with the added bonus of NO HOA fees. As you step inside, the heart of this home is revealed in the well-designed kitchen. Equipped with a convenient gas range, ample counter space, and generous cabinet storage, it's a perfect space for culinary adventures and family gatherings. The converted garage adds a unique touch, providing the ideal flex space for your needs. Whether you envision it as a cozy family room, a lively game room, a productive home office, or any combination thereof – the possibilities are endless. A fireplace adds warmth and character to this versatile area. Take a moment to unwind on the inviting front porch, where you can soak in the sights and sounds of the friendly neighborhood. For those who love outdoor entertaining, the back enclosed patio with an attached patio is an ideal spot. Relax and enjoy the fenced-in backyard, complete with a convenient storage shed. This home goes above and beyond with modern features, including solar panels and a Generac whole-home generator for added peace of mind. Practicality meets sustainability, ensuring your comfort and security. Conveniently located off of 701, you're just minutes away from Downtown Conway, the scenic Conway Riverwalk, excellent golfing facilities, shopping destinations, diverse dining options, and exciting entertainment venues. Embrace the best of both worlds – a tranquil home retreat with easy access to the vibrant amenities Conway has to offer. Book your showing today!
